java.lang.Object

public class TraceRelationshipBuilder<K>
extends java.lang.Object

TraceRelationshipBuilder is a helper for building Trace instances.

This class is not thread-safe.

Chris Pettitt (cpettitt@linkedin.com), Chi Chan (ckchan@linkedin.com)
